org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface ICommonClassNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IDefinitionNode, IDocumentableDefinitionNode, IScopedDefinitionNode, ISourceLocation, ITypeNode
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IClassNode, IMXMLApplicationNode, IMXMLClassDefinitionNode, IMXMLDocumentNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClassNode, MXMLClassDefinitionNode, MXMLDocumentNode

    public interface ICommonClassNode
extends ITypeNode, IDocumentableDefinitionNode
    This interface contains the APIs that are available for both ActionScript and MXML class nodes.

    IClassNode extends this with APIs specific to AS trees and IMXMLClassDefinitionNode extends this with APIs specific to MXML trees.

      • getMetaTagsByName

        IMetaTag[] getMetaTagsByName(String name)
        Retrieve all of the meta attributes (e.g. [Event("")]) that match the given name in the metadata for this class. This does not walk up the inehritance chain.
        Parameters:
        name - name of meta attributes to search for (e.g. Event or IconFile)
